{"tid":1024036,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"學生會正副會長是藏人和台灣人！加拿大中國留學生崩潰喊「當選無效」","createTime":"2019-02-16T08:50:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-17T14:49:22.000Z","uid":47714,"like":48,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"c75636c9055e6ace45cb865323306cb99e88595b","tid":1024036,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T08:50:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.dopost.com/articles-3/20190213-1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dopost.com%2Farticles-3%2F20190213-1&d=gHg%2Fa1kZgicCxdd1JZL7L39Z9R%2B5WvgLevJIGZbvuGo%3D&h=498f1cef\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dopost.com/articles-3/20190213-1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static1.squarespace.com/static/5abd8f50e17ba366312a1158/5abdb9f6758d46a7b61c881d/5c62edbdc830255be3ec2d70/1549990209012/台灣人學生會副會長.png?format=1500w\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic1.squarespace.com%2Fstatic%2F5abd8f50e17ba366312a1158%2F5abdb9f6758d46a7b61c881d%2F5c62edbdc830255be3ec2d70%2F1549990209012%2F%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E4%BA%BA%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%9C%83%E5%89%AF%E6%9C%83%E9%95%B7.png%3Fformat%3D1500w&h=1ed2d362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n加拿大多倫多大學士嘉堡分校近期舉行學生會長選舉，當選的會長是藏裔的拉莫（Chemi Lhamo），由於其公開主張西藏獨立，讓中國留學生崩潰透過知名請願網站《<a href=\"http://Change.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FChange.org&d=gHg%2Fa1kZgicCxdd1JZL7L39Z9R%2B5WvgLevJIGZbvuGo%3D&h=a0422e71\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Change.org</a>》發動連署，要校方判決拉莫「當選無效」。如今，卻有批踢踢網友發現，不只會長是藏人會讓中國留學生崩潰，副會長更是來自台灣的蔡禮陽（Leon Tsai）。<br />\n<br />\n拉莫當選後，個人Instagram（<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/chemilhamoooo/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;ig_mid=W9sf4gABAAEvHgLxC4gl-xeN-NlQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fchemilhamoooo%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26ig_mid%3DW9sf4gABAAEvHgLxC4gl-xeN-NlQ&d=gHg%2Fa1kZgicCxdd1JZL7L39Z9R%2B5WvgLevJIGZbvuGo%3D&h=efdbb13d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/chemilhamoooo/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;ig_mid=W9sf4gABAAEvHgLxC4gl-xeN-NlQ</a>）隨即遭到眾多中國網友謾罵，批評她支持西藏獨立，「有本事回中國舉藏獨旗」、「但你如果真想獨立，那就打仗，你覺得你能打贏？」，但很快就有來自香港及台灣的網民留言反擊，「為什麼寧可做海外華人，不回國貢獻，支那人講一套做一套」、「香港人支持你，Support From Hong Kong」。<br />\n<br />\n根據批踢踢網友表示，這次嘉堡分校學生會正副會長的主要競爭者，主要自由主義與保守主義之爭。會長選舉方面，代表自由主義的拉莫是西藏獨立的支持者，獲得白人及來自非洲、亞洲跟印度同學普遍支持；代表保守主義的Anup Atwal則獲得中東跟非洲穆斯林族群跟中國留學生支持。而副會長選舉方面，代表自由主義的是來自台灣的蔡禮陽，他是LGBTQ支持者，並且形象正面很受歡迎；代表保守主義的則是Chaman Bukhari，他是穆斯林，反對LGBTQ，獲得中東，北非穆斯林族群跟中國留學生支持。最後，由拉莫跟蔡禮陽分別當選正副會長。<br />\n<br />\n該篇貼文分析，中東穆斯林與中國留學生合作，已造成一些土耳其穆斯林學生差點抓狂，他們雖然不是很能接受LGBTQ，但是絕對無法跟中國留學生妥協，原因是中國政府對待新疆維吾爾族的議題上。<br />\n<br />\n根據香港《立場新聞》報導，多倫多大學在2017至18年度共有90,077名學生，其中來自中國的留學生（不含港澳）佔11,544人，在留學生中佔最大比例。而該校的香港留學生及台灣留學生，則分別有357人及277人。<br />\n<br />\n報導還指出，多倫多大學是加拿大最頂尖學府，在去年QS世界大學排名中排名世界第31位，而它在多項世界大學排名中，均被冠為加拿大第一學府。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10156896254422357\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcheng.lap.9%2Fposts%2F10156896254422357&d=gHg%2Fa1kZgicCxdd1JZL7L39Z9R%2B5WvgLevJIGZbvuGo%3D&h=03ce6b94\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10156896254422357</a><br />\n<br />\n花影:<br />\n西藏留學加拿大女生拉莫，競選多倫多大學士嘉堡區學生會主席，<a href=\"http://遭中共國同學於change.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E9%81%AD%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%B1%E5%9C%8B%E5%90%8C%E5%AD%B8%E6%96%BCchange.org&d=gHg%2Fa1kZgicCxdd1JZL7L39Z9R%2B5WvgLevJIGZbvuGo%3D&h=443e8fc2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">遭中共國同學於change.org</a>發起杯葛，並已收到一萬個簽名。此時，<a href=\"http://亦有人在change.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E4%BA%A6%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%BA%E5%9C%A8change.org&d=gHg%2Fa1kZgicCxdd1JZL7L39Z9R%2B5WvgLevJIGZbvuGo%3D&h=e78ef4bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">亦有人在change.org</a>收集簽名，支持拉莫。我希望尊重學術，反對留學生將中共國價值觀植入加拿大學府的朋友，能夠簽名送上我們的支持，並請廣傳！ <a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/university-of-toronto-scarborough-let-chemi-remain-as-student-union-presidential-candidate\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Funiversity-of-toronto-scarborough-let-chemi-remain-as-student-union-presidential-candidate&d=gHg%2Fa1kZgicCxdd1JZL7L39Z9R%2B5WvgLevJIGZbvuGo%3D&h=5d611ac3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/university-of-toronto-scarborough-let-chemi-remain-as-student-union-presidential-candidate</a>"},{"pid":"3754ccd6523766887277b66057405da5cffd5077","tid":1024036,"uid":35790,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T08:52:06.000Z","msg":"搵人大釋法DQ囉<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afd45a020b70e33b507ddae13f9a76aca16d72bf","tid":1024036,"uid":15274,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T08:55:26.000Z","msg":"9萬位學生有超過1萬既係支那人<br />\n真係蝗禍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"570eed76d07fc9826b382943c929112ab7cc88ca","tid":1024036,"uid":28195,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"afd45a020b70e33b507ddae13f9a76aca16d72bf","tid":1024036,"uid":15274,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T08:55:26.000Z","msg":"9萬位學生有超過1萬既係支那人<br />\n真係蝗禍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T08:59:18.000Z","msg":"90年代初，得香港人移民去加拿大，當時真係清泉一般<br />\n<br />\n依家周圍都係蝗，好多問題才發生"},{"pid":"60968c04f5b974ba85e89987c878e64e2c9a5e1e","tid":1024036,"uid":35790,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T09:01:50.000Z","msg":"支那邏輯：<br />\n西藏人 台灣人都係中華民族<br />\n大家都係中國人<br />\n<br />\n相煎可太急<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"598c2bfba0c488be9d643e4f3a6ccf7baef68b44","tid":1024036,"uid":128600,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T09:03:08.000Z","msg":"你話冇效就冇效咁選來做咩？"},{"pid":"5dbeeba671799041e2367e8cb4734b6ee26db7a1","tid":1024036,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T09:17:03.000Z","msg":"全世界都圍住支那嚟轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=